import './App.css'
import { BrowserRouter as Router, Routes, Route } from 'react-router-dom'
import AuntificationPage from './components/Auntification/AuntificationPage'
import React from 'react'
import AuntifactionPageCallback from './components/Auntification/AuntifactionPageCallback'

import { SocketProvider } from './components/Context/SocketContext'
import io from 'socket.io-client'
const socket = io('http://localhost:3005')
function App() {
	return (
		<SocketProvider>
			<AuntificationPage />

			<Routes>
				<Route path='/auntification' element={<AuntifactionPageCallback />} />
				
			
			</Routes>
		</SocketProvider>
	)
}

export default App
